Abjuration
Level: Blk 1, Pal 1 (Red Knight)
Components: V
Casting Time: 1 action
Range: Personal
Target: You
Duration: 1 round/level

You gain the benefits of the Mobility feat, even if you do not meet the prerequisites.  You do not have to be charging to gain the benefit.  Originally granted by the Red Knight to his paladins, other faiths now have a version of this spell.